cutrgl                  Cutting a rectangular region from an rgl plot.
image2Drgl              2-D image, contour, scatterplots, segments and
                        arrows in rgl.
persp3Drgl              3-D plotting functions using rgl.
plot3Drgl-package       Functions to plot multi-dimensional data using
                        'rgl'.
plotrgl                 Plot 3D graphs in rgl window.
